{"tid":2055740,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"網隊親中班主允主場設連儂牆 去年曾批火箭總經理撐香港民主運動","createTime":"2020-06-08T07:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T08:16:04.000Z","uid":9030,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ea742e5977fe32d1b7a769eb48295f14c9cc25d","tid":2055740,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:47:28.000Z","msg":"有人把網隊主場巴克萊中心外牆當作連儂牆，寫下自己的聲音。網隊台灣籍班主蔡崇信（Joe Tsai）周日發聲明指，接受大家在球館外的和平示威。<br />\n<br />\n巴克萊中心外牆被市民用粉筆寫下訴求，如「除止殺害我們」、「警察殺人該向誰求救」、「我們需要愛」等的字句，也有人用油畫的方式表達聲音，猶如香港的連儂牆。<br />\n<br />\n網隊班主蔡崇信，發聲明指只要示威是和平的，他願意讓球場成為大家表達訴求的地方。惟去年火箭總經理莫利（Daryl Morey）發文支持香港民主運動，蔡崇信在FB發長文指，莫利的言論涉及中國分離主義，損害到中國人民的感情。來自台灣的他，家鄉也跟中國有着敏感的兩岸政治，但這位內地企業集團阿里巴巴共同創辦人兼執行副主席認為，談及中國領土完整和國家主權問題時，是沒有商討的餘地。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200608/WUIXIC6R7RAFDPXD77BJNRVK5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200608%2FWUIXIC6R7RAFDPXD77BJNRVK5Y%2F&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=ceb44a56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200608%2FWUIXIC6R7RAFDPXD77BJNRVK5Y%2F&h=2ff7d821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200608/WUIXIC6R7RAFDPXD77BJNRVK5Y/</a>"},{"pid":"7b4f3a39804589f88adc8bfd109b079d1b9ec351","tid":2055740,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:50:58.000Z","msg":"錢作怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af383addbfb8c664e2b7017aa4e359eb1bded5f","tid":2055740,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:52:36.000Z","msg":"因為今次關美國同黑人試"},{"pid":"d6bf7805a40881ad67d49c1ad0fe5cbbeea690a1","tid":2055740,"uid":9030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b4f3a39804589f88adc8bfd109b079d1b9ec351","tid":2055740,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T07:50:58.000Z","msg":"錢作怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:16:04.000Z","msg":"損害自己利益就屌人發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}